How to contribute

Reporting bugs

If you find a bug in daiR, please report it on the issue tracker.

Suggesting enhancements

If you want to suggest a new feature or an improvement of a current feature, you can submit this on the issue tracker.

Reporting other problems

If you encounter a problem using daiR and are not sure what the source of the problem is, you can report this too on the issue tracker

Submitting a pull request

If you want to directly submit code to daiR, you can do this by forking the daiR repo and then submitting a pull request.

Code of conduct

We expect all our contributors to follow the Contributor Covenant. Any unacceptable behaviour can be reported to Thomas (hegghammer@gmail.com).
